          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/>
            </svg>
            Accommodation & rooming lists
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/>
            </svg>
            Travel planning (multi-segment)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/>
            </svg>
            Event vehicle management
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a
